description.excerpt: This project aims to detect emotions on faces. First it detects faces with haarcascade classifier or with MTCNN model, then through a convolutionnal network it classifies the emotion from seven categories {'angry', 'disgust', 'fear', 'happy', 'sad', 'surprise', 'neutral'}. To train the model we had two choices of dataset : FER2013 and CK+48. In this version, the model is trained with FER2013 dataset and it uses MTCNN model to detect faces.
